headline: Incyte's Rare Blood Cancer Therapy Gets FDA's Breakthrough Status
summary: INCY secures FDA Breakthrough Therapy status for INCA033989 after early data show rapid and sustained platelet normalization in essential thrombocythemia patients.

headline: Incyte Stock Falls Despite FDA Breakthrough Therapy Fast Track For Rare Blood Cancer Drug
summary: The FDA granted Breakthrough Therapy status to Incyte's experimental treatment for a rare blood cancer. Incyte stock fell from near five-year highs.
